\c 24 Jobho haanzwisisi kuti vatadzi vanoregereiko kurohwa 24 1 WaMasimbaose anoregereiko kutara nguva dzokutonga? Vanomuziva vanoregereiko kuona mazuva ake? 2 Vanoshandura miganho varipo; Vanopamba mapoka amakwai, vachiafudza. 3 Vanotinha mbongoro yenherera, Vanotora nzombe yechirikadzi vachiita rubatso. 4 Vanodzinga varombo panzira; Varombo venyika vanovanda vose. 5 Tarira, sembizi murenje Vanobudira kumabasa avo, vachishingairira zvokwadi; Renje rinovapa zvokudya zvavana vavo. 6 Vanocheka zvavanodya kusango; Vanounganidza madzambiringa avakaipa. 7 Vanovata usiku hwose vasina zvavakafuka,
